ZH: 姥爷每天都会去公园散步。
EN: Grandpa goes for a walk in the park every day.

ZH: 我的姥爷是一位老医生。
EN: My grandpa is a retired doctor.

ZH: 姥爷喜欢在花园里种花。
EN: Grandpa likes to plant flowers in the garden.

ZH: 姥爷喜欢给我们讲故事。
EN: Grandpa likes to tell us stories.

ZH: 我们全家都会聚在姥爷家里过年。
EN: Our whole family gathers at grandpa's house for Chinese New Year.

ZH: 姥爷是我们家的顶梁柱。
EN: Grandpa is the pillar of our family.

ZH: 姥爷非常喜欢在农村生活。
EN: Grandpa loves living in the countryside.

ZH: 每次看见姥爷，我都觉得很开心。
EN: I feel happy every time I see grandpa.

ZH: 姥爷的爱好是钓鱼。
EN: Grandpa's hobby is fishing.

ZH: 姥爷喜欢穿他的军装。
EN: Grandpa likes to wear his military uniform.

ZH: 姥爷有一个很大的花园。
EN: Grandpa has a very large garden.

ZH: 姥爷年轻的时候是一名战士。
EN: Grandpa was a soldier when he was young.

ZH: 她想念她家的姥爷。
EN: She misses her grandpa.

ZH: 姥爷喜欢吹着口琴。
EN: Grandpa likes to play the harmonica.

ZH: 姥爷跟我们说过很多关于他年轻时的故事。
EN: Grandpa has told us many stories about his youth.

ZH: 姥爷的眼睛里充满了智慧。
EN: Grandpa's eyes are full of wisdom.

ZH: 姥爷的厨艺很好，经常给我们做好吃的菜。
EN: Grandpa is a good cook and often makes delicious dishes for us.

ZH: 姥爷住在离我们家很远的地方。
EN: Grandpa lives far away from our house.

ZH: 姥爷总是给我们带来好吃的糖果。
EN: Grandpa always brings us delicious candies.

ZH: 姥爷很喜欢唱歌，尤其是小曲儿。
EN: Grandpa loves singing, especially folk songs.
